# Assistant Tools

- Add each assistant tool as exactly one module in `src/lib/assistant-tools/tools`.
- Each module must export a default `AssistantToolModule` with `key`, `description`, and `createTool(runtime)`.
- Keep the LLM-facing tool description in the same file as the implementation.
- Do not store assistant tool definitions or descriptions in Prisma.
- Use `listAssistantTools()` for tool lists and `createAssistantTools(runtime)` for the `streamText` tool set.
- Update `src/lib/assistant-tools/README.md` if the tool contract changes.
